  "content": "# Nodes\n\nThis directory contains both canonical XanaNode nodes and local extension nodes.\n\nThe file `memex-illustration.json` uses the custom node type:\n\n```text\nexample.museum:artifact\n```\n\nBecause the type is namespaced and declared in `schemas/`, other substrates can preserve it even when they do not natively support museum artifacts.\n",
